# Hamnix hpm repo trust root — Ed25519 public key (32 bytes, hex).
#
# hpm verifies the DETACHED signature index.json.sig against this key
# before trusting any hash in a fetched index.json (see user/hpm.ad and
# lib/ed25519.ad). The same 32 bytes are compiled into the hpm binary as
# the built-in default trust root; this file lets an operator inspect or
# rotate the trusted key without recompiling. The matching SECRET key is
# held out of band by the repo operator and is NEVER committed — the
# build signs with scripts/hpm_sign.py when HPM_REPO_SECKEY points at it.
#
# Lines beginning with '#' are comments; the first bare token is the key.
87c67427ce90c5f12718b3ee8fbc7bb8edd164b9ad3a3a7bc613999f00eb336f
